translations: 公寓房间（tenement 的复数形式）

sentences.sentence: Many of the old Victorian tenements were gone and whole areas now required rebuilding.
sentences.translation: 很多维多利亚时代的古老建筑已经消失不见，现在整个区域亟待重建。

sentences.sentence: For those that rent, nearly all tenements have loans, which will also be written off.
sentences.translation: 对那些出租情况来说，几乎所有的出租房都有租金，这些也将被取消。

sentences.sentence: Extensive Uranium anomalism on active tenements yet to be suitably explored and delineated.
sentences.translation: 有效租约区内存在大量的铀异常现象，这些租约区尚未进行适当的勘探和描述。
